Information, Memory and Manipulation\
\
1. Trump administration officials left sensitive State Department documents on a public hotel printer and then falsely downplayed them as a lunch menu (2025-08-16): Mishandling and then misrepresenting sensitive diplomatic documents undermined basic information security and public confidence in the government\'92s candor about national security lapses.\
